{"tid":1920264,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"擇洗溝宅男","createTime":"2020-03-11T10:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T14:03:13.000Z","uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"093fb17b2e10358aaeeb5f8292e8a54146afeb30","tid":1920264,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:46:48.000Z","msg":"討論電影=&gt; 極地守護犬 &amp; 擇洗溝宅男<br />\n<br />\n極地守護犬=&gt; <br />\n主要分兩個故事, 前半送郵件, 後半老人與狗.<br />\n整體兒童向, CG幾好因為狗同動物應該都係電腦CG來.<br />\n整體都算睇得開開心心.<br />\n但想睇福伯會有D失望,因下半場先擔正,上半場只係客串.<br />\n<br />\n純粹解悶可以一看.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=MdCfDgXxM4U&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D2%26v%3DMdCfDgXxM4U%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stgHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=728dd31a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=MdCfDgXxM4U&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n擇洗溝宅男 =&gt; <br />\n戲名古怪唔知點解改呢個名.<br />\n基本一部宅男愛情故事. 亦都瘋刺現代人已經活在5.5吋世界次中.<br />\n男主角演技出色,因為好多時都係同手機做對手戲.<br />\n無悶場,都幾多笑位.不過較多不文笑話,同有男人雀仔鏡頭(1,2 個shot)!!<br />\n<br />\n如果2選1,會建議看擇洗溝宅男.<br />\n因為比較特別, 主角演得幾好.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZSUCS9EOjSw&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZSUCS9EOjSw%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stgHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=082a9cc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZSUCS9EOjSw&amp;feature=emb_logo</a>"},{"pid":"58e3eaf9c0f76602e7fa2765daf984e45a3c1fe1","tid":1920264,"uid":8247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"擇洗溝宅男<br />\n擇洗應該係食JEXI個音"},{"pid":"e48658929e0297ed037fecfac2832209a376b661","tid":1920264,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"睇狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif